Kernel, boot firmware, devices and hacks for Raspberry Pi

This script will build the following packages:
  raspi-boot
  raspi-devs
  raspi-hacks
  kernel_raspi
  kernel-modules-raspi

Before running this script, $CWD/linux and $CWD/firmware must contain these
git repos:
  git clone git://github.com/raspberrypi/linux.git linux
  git clone git://github.com/raspberrypi/firmware.git firmware
